\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  the outcome at the end. I wrote it all down very neatly.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I showed my plan to Mrs. Scullery, and she was very pleased. She even smiled at me and said, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Well done, Mina. That is very good, dear. Now you may write the story.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 But of course when I started to \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 write, the story wouldn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t keep still, wouldn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
