\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 I mean it wanted to do othe\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 r things, Miss.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 She put her hands on her hips and shook her head. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It is a story,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  she said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It is your story. It will do what you tell it to.\'94
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 But it won\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t,\'94\loch\f0  I said. She kept on glaring at me.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 And Miss,\'94\loch\f0  I said, like I was pleading with her to underst\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 and. \'93\loch\f0 I don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t want it to, Miss.\'94
