\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 Heaven. I used to think that the idea of Heaven was silly. I used to think of all the people who keep on dying. Heaven must get ridiculously full, I thought. There wouldn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
