\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 hands and sang a lullaby to it. I squashed the clay together and started again and I made an archaeopteryx.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 The archaeopteryx was a dinosaur, a dinosaur with wings and feathers. It could fly. Probably not as well as birds can now. It was a bony thing, and \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 
