s the ancestor of all the birds that exist in the world today. The blackbirds building their nest in the tree above my head are its descen\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 d\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 ants!
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 There are archaeopteryx fossils in the Natural History Museum in London. Mum has said we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll go to see them, when she has a bit of time, and a bit of money.
