t afford a proper kiln, so the things we make go in with loaves of bread and casseroles and pizzas and curries, so they never get properly baked or properly glazed.\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 That doesn\hich\f0 \rquote 
