 it looks nothing like him, of course, at least not when I c\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 o\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 mpare it with his photographs, but somehow it seems to be more like him than the photographs do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
