n I was small (funny how writing like this makes me keep thinking about what I was like when I was small) and still at school. There was an Art lesson and I got carried away. We were using plasticine in Mrs. Tompkinson\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
s Art class and I made a little man.\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 I made him walk along my desk. When I thought nobody was looking I picked him up and started whispering into his ear.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Come alive!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  I whispered. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Come alive!\'94
