t remember. I tried very hard to put them all out of my brain). I caught him looking at me. I stared back like I was asking him, \'93\loch\f0 What do you think you\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re looking at?\'94\loch\f0 
 He shook his head like he thought I was crazy. I pointed a finger at him \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 a\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 nd waggled it and I rolled my eyes like I was putting a spell on him.
