 . My mum is a fantastic cook! We went out for a walk. I told Mum about the blackbirds\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0  nest and about Mr. Myers\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s daughter. His house looked so dirty and dark as we passed by it.
