\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Met-em-sy-co-sis,\'94\loch\f0  she said, more slowly.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Me-tem-sy-co-sis!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  I said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What a fantastic word! Metempsychosis! Metempsychosis! Met-em-sy-beautiful-co-sis!\'94
