\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 I smiled back at her. It was lovely to think of being in Grace\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s dream.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 Isn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t it funny,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  she said. \'93\loch\f0 I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 d forgotten all about it, and suddenly it all flood\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 
ed back. Ah, well. That\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s how dreams go.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 She squeezed my hands again. She took a deep breath and winced.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 She will come back again, Mina,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  she said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 She always does.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 She tugged her scarf tighter on her throat.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Got to keep moving,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  she said. \'93\loch\f0 Bye-bye, M\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ina.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  She winked. \'93\loch\f0 Maybe I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
