\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 She left the street. I \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 thought about being in her dream. It was very strange. Maybe we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 re all in somebody\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s dream. Maybe everything\hich\f0 
