\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 She shrugged.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 So strange, I suppose,\'94\loch\f0  she said.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Am I?\'94
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Kind of. A bit kind of complicated.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 I looked at the kids in the yard, running round together, hanging out together.
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 I don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t mean to be,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  I said. I laughed. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Maybe I should have an operation to fix it.\'94
